ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectReserve Creation - Metepenagiag Mi'kmaq Nation - Metepenagiag Urban reserve 8, New Brunswick
PrecisOrder setting apart 3.58 hectares (8.85 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Metepenagiag Mi'kmaq Nation, as a new reserve to be known as METEPENAGIAG URBAN RESERVE 8, in New Brunswick.
